		y: 2.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000000A03D"]
		title: "The Herb Garden"
		icon: {id: "soulland:wild_herb", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Spirit Herbs grow in patches across the world — Wild Herb, Spirit Grass, Spirit Flower, Cloud Mushroom, Spirit Mushroom. Most feed into the cultivation pill system at the Forging Table.", "Gather everything you see. Some rare pills require herbs that only spawn in specific biomes or in limited patches. Don't pass one without picking it."]
