		title: "Space Ring"
		icon: {id: "soulland:space_ring_basic", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Space Ring is an inventory expansion item that equips in your Curios ring slot. Stack it with the Artifacts mod rings and your Sophisticated Backpack and the inventory problem stops being a problem.", "There are four tiers: Basic, Enhanced, Superior, Legendary. Start with Basic. Upgrade when you can craft the next tier at the Forging Table. The Legendary tier holds an absurd amount."]
